snippet.textDisplay:
Respect to all the artists on video and off video. 
But sad to say Coke studio is loosing its fundamental. The purity is gone. The analog purity is gone. Why are there dancers in video. Show the live band performance. Even if it’s a digital music show it to public how it is done, it will inspire budding artists. 
Otherwise please tell me how is this video different than artists creating their private album. What is the uniqueness of coke studio?
